er reaches the stock room, the reality of it all hits her and she breaks down into a anxiety attack and cowers in the corner while my drifter bleeds out. My chef breaks and goes bezerk, looking for anything moving to shoot with his new bow. The warg wanders aimlessly into the area and gets a final arrow in him and falls unconscious to the ground to bleed out.I saved the game under another name with my engineer cowering in the stockroom and the chef roaming the base in a bezerk state...10/10 would experience the horror again."
