 to blast off, and as I'm about to do it this giant raid comes my way with 30 raiders ready to pillage and murder everything that crossed their way so I hastily got my remaining colonists inside and blasted off just as the raiders were getting through my defenses. And this ladies and gentlemen was one story among so many others, the AI driven storyteller does a really amazing job, one of the best, if not the best, AI I've ever had the pleasure facing in any game.If you liked what you read please do buy the game, this developer deserves it and this game sure as hell does too.Thank you for your time.PS: It seems I might have stayed up playing for too long, the sun is rising."
