 find that somehow his liver had been punctured (wtf José really???) and his torso was badly cut. He soon died, and the other colonists minds broke as well.It was chaos and for one night, the were all…...free….…. Running off into the wilderness they somehow found themselves, lost out there, among the wildlife. I wept for Hammer. For Silver. For José, you beautiful ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥. For the less important characters without names, many of whom died horrific deaths as they lost their minds snapped like twigs with the weight of the void pressing down on them.10/10 I didn’t know if it would be worth $30.It is."
