ers and you can take people prisoners.Winter/Summer Season and Day/Night Cyclus.Save and load game is available.Other things.I am not a huge fan of early access, In fact i do not buy a game really from the EA. But I have checked some videos and this game got my attention. They update and they are still active. This game has a huge potential and super entertaining and it is worth any penny.-------------------I Give this game a 9/10"
