,Recommended,294100,31382996,Posted: 26 April,all,Shojun94,"Rimwordaka GoddbyeSocialLifeAs I'm sure you all know, buying an early access game is always a risk: all gamers have had investments ruined by eitherabandonware,terrible releasesor unaccomplished promises. When you look at a game like Rimworld and it's relatively steep price (aprox. $30/€28) you can't hope but ponder if you're not walking into another devtrap.I bought this game for a relatively low price compared to this in a sale and decided to take my chances and thus I started a gamer's romance that lasts until today.You will get your money's worth!Gameplay conceptLink: gameplay videoThe game consists of asandbox survival, colony management game with light roleplay elements. You're tasked with assuring the survival of a number of random colonists/refugees while optionally attempting to escape the planet. It is highly mod-friendly and throws you into an inhabited alien world with all kinds of earthly and otherworldy creatures, plant life, friendly and vicious humans.Your gameplay difficulty will be affected by the climate of the area you choose to settle in, the storyteller (difficulty meter) and starting conditions.Research will allow access to higher tiers of technology with more powerful weapons, farming methods, power generators, etc..Each colonist and even animal is subject to complex psychological processes like personality traits and mood swings, medical conditions, needs and relationships. Think of it as a kick♥♥♥♥♥TheSims in an alien world.ModdingThe game supports steam workshop!!There are mods ranging from additional content like automated and hand operated turrets to carpets, medical technology and additional prosthesis, creatures and cults fromH. P. Lovecraft, high-end technology, additional tribe/medieval life technology... guys, there are loads of mods, ok? After a couple of replays you can change the game into something completely different.CommunityYou can find streams on Twitch and Steam with players from all over the world. For some reason, making nudist colonies (safe for work) is becoming highly popular...Other aspectsThe sound isawesome. Great music, great atmosphere.The graphics areawesome. Simple but awesome, somewhat similar to Prison Architect.Everything isawesome!So...Feel free to comment or message me for questions! I regularly stream on Twitch with tutorial gameplays, feel free to message me and I'll come online and help you out!A special note of thanks to the developers for this great game, the community for the mods and streams and my GF for not remembering my face when I go on a Rimworld binge."
