he, a muffalo had self tamed and then eaten most of the healroot. George attempted to harvest the remaining healroot and failed so the healer died. George, who was already stressed from everything that happened, and one can only assume, well earned self-hatred, went insane and starved to death.Tired of all the problems the men had caused me, I started a new colony with only women and added the condition that the were all gay. One ended up being a pyromaniac and burned the place down."
