76561198105410749,Recommended,294100,33198570,Posted: 3 July,all,Rochmaister,One of the few colony sims that hit the golden spot between complex enough to be interesting and simple enough to not be a pain in the♥♥♥♥♥♥to learn. I also happen to like the artstyle but that's up for debate. Interesting to play in sessions usually spaced by at least a few weeks.
