al she was holding. She traded 64 silver for it, and ate it immediately, saving none for anyone else. Because of this, Legua flew into a binge eating state, and tore into Val's still twitching corpse.That night:Cody was starving to death. If she did not send the lavish meal to ge eaten by strangers, she would still have her life. Before she went to bed, (a hard wooden floor) she snapped. She got up like the pessimist she was, and screamed out, waking her friend who's name has been long forgotten. She pumped Cody full of bullets, but not before Cody ripped her eye out. She quickly stumbled out the border of the territory.Legua screamed in pain after the procedures, screams that were more annoying than anything to Gabella. She sighed, and pulled out her pemmican. Proud of what she had done.10/10This is the best game I hav ever played!"
